    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Chickenauts》是一款以同伴为特色的动作轻度Rogue游戏。与种类繁多且战力强大的变异鸡同伴一起，在随机化的巨型外星母舰上杀出一条路吧。<br><br>一切开始于一帮烦人的外星人降落在了你农场外面，并抓走了你所有的鸡用来进行各种离谱的基因实验！<br><br>拿上你的枪，带上大杀器变异鸡同伴，狠狠教训那些擅闯私人领地的外星混蛋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/dbb4fd68d3d41981e1f954f4b2b6d23c.avif?t=1772035654\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/566b7b32bc089a45e71dd4fb60d319fc.poster.avif?t=1772035654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/566b7b32bc089a45e71dd4fb60d319fc.webm?t=1772035654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/566b7b32bc089a45e71dd4fb60d319fc.mp4?t=1772035654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在每一轮游戏里，你都能培养出独特的大杀器同伴。 <br><br>在教训外星混蛋的过程中，你可以解救、武装鸡同伴并使其变异，它们和你一样想要报复并消灭外星人。每只鸡同伴的灵感都源于流行文化标志性要素，并拥有迥然不同的特性与能力。<br><br>一路上你可以选择多种可叠加的变异，每轮游戏都可以培养出强到破坏游戏平衡的大杀器鸡同伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/b9995ef8265c2a32fcb287228236dd04.avif?t=1772035654\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/df126043ea94950c83fb75cb0daeb215.poster.avif?t=1772035654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/df126043ea94950c83fb75cb0daeb215.webm?t=1772035654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/df126043ea94950c83fb75cb0daeb215.mp4?t=1772035654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>每一轮都带来独特的游戏体验。 <br><br>以短、频、快为特色的每轮游戏由随机化的紧凑房间组成，每个房间只需不到一分钟即可肃清。<br><br>你将迎战种类繁多的怪物鸡小怪和首领，每场战斗都不重样。房间、生成的敌人、所有变异、升级和掉落的战利品都是随机化的，因此每轮游戏都充满变数，并鼓励玩家多尝试不同的玩法。<br><br>就算失败，也不用气馁。收集到的鸡蛋、武器以及解锁的同伴都会在以后的游戏中生效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/5bcf38e5a8d373a88e1cd4fc898863ef.avif?t=1772035654\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/337f843d844e33728e56c72ee5d00ba1.poster.avif?t=1772035654\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/337f843d844e33728e56c72ee5d00ba1.webm?t=1772035654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350460/extras/337f843d844e33728e56c72ee5d00ba1.mp4?t=1772035654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>- 每局游戏耗时短但紧张刺激。每个房间只需不到一分钟即可肃清。 <br>- 一系列灵感源于流行文化的同伴，每只都拥有不同的能力。<br>- 每轮都能用随机化且可叠加的能力来使同伴变异。<br>- 多种多样的小怪和首领<br>- 随机化的房间、敌人、变异、升级以及战利品掉落<br>- 每轮都能有所成长。</p>",
